java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<SbbInvocationState>
public enum SbbInvocationState
extends java.lang.Enum<SbbInvocationState>

This class represents the Invocation State of an sbb object It is used in rollback handling to determine what to do since this depends on whether an sbb object method invocation was happening at the time the exception was thrown

Author:
Tim, martins
